title: [Vornavian Coast, South Beach]
description: A huge crate has washed ashore here, possibly brought in by a storm.  The crate lies well inland from the surf, and has been bleached near-white by the constant sun.

A huge crate has washed ashore here, possibly brought in by a storm.  The crate lies well inland from the surf, and has been bleached near-white by the constant sun.  A seagull perches atop the crate, glaring at other gulls as they approach.
